Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.36,0:01:31.45,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}僕ら晴る風
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.45,0:01:35.78,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}あの雲も越えてゆけ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.78,0:01:40.71,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}遠くまだ遠くまで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.21,0:00:27.01,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}你就像風一般
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.01,0:00:31.39,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}閉上眼 已是黃昏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.76,0:00:37.23,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}你在想些什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.11,0:00:45.90,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}睜開雙眼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.90,0:00:50.15,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}你的眼眸晶瑩透亮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.45,0:00:57.33,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}散發著絲絲晴的氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.25,0:01:08.46,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}晴空萬里 花開遍地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.46,0:01:12.68,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}百花皆為晴而開
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.68,0:01:17.06,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}就連初晴後的雨滴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.06,0:01:21.73,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}也是裝飾於你的晴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.06,0:01:27.36,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}心中的悸動啊化作細風
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.36,0:01:31.45,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}我們亦化為晴風
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.45,0:01:35.78,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}穿過那片雲彩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.78,0:01:40.71,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}直到天邊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.89,0:22:33.79,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fscx90\fscy90\fad(360,360)\blur3}And you alright
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.92,0:22:36.78,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fscx90\fscy90\fad(360,360)\blur3}Can you hear me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.71,0:22:43.46,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fscx90\fscy90\fad(360,360)\blur3}誰もいない線路沿いをなぞってく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.81,0:22:45.93,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fscx90\fscy90\fad(360,360)\blur3}大袈裟に泣いて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.71,0:22:48.75,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fscx90\fscy90\fad(360,360)\blur3}笑ってほしくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.38,0:22:55.24,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fscx90\fscy90\fad(360,360)\blur3}鮮明でいたい思い出を抱きしめている
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.24,0:23:01.63,ED_JP,,0,0,40,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}さよならよりずっと大切な　言葉で伝えたいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.63,0:23:07.40,ED_JP,,0,0,40,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}ありふれて　でも特別で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.40,0:23:10.92,ED_JP,,0,0,40,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}ほら　この目じゃなければ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.92,0:23:13.89,ED_JP,,0,0,40,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}見えなかったものが
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.89,0:23:18.71,ED_JP,,0,0,40,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}どうして？　溢れてく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.71,0:23:24.72,ED_JP,,0,0,40,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}だから　もう一度　生まれ変わろうとも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.90,0:23:30.64,ED_JP,,0,0,40,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}また　私はここを選ぶんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.64,0:23:36.64,ED_JP,,0,0,40,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}だから　あなたと　また巡り逢ったら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.64,0:23:42.32,ED_JP,,0,0,40,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}もう離さない　今を選ぶんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.32,0:23:45.22,ED_JP,,0,0,40,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}約束なんてなくても
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.22,0:23:48.32,ED_JP,,0,0,40,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}孤独に迷う日々でも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.32,0:23:54.31,ED_JP,,0,0,40,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}その涙だって大丈夫　きっと夜が明けるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.54,0:23:58.54,ED_JP,,0,0,40,,{\fad(360,0)\blur3}I’m whispering our lullaby for you to come back home
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.54,0:24:01.35,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fscx90\fscy90\fad(0,360)\blur3}I’m whispering our lullaby for you to come back home
Dialogue: 1,0:22:31.89,0:22:33.79,ED_CH,,0,0,65,,{\an9\fscx90\fscy90\fad(360,360)\blur3}你還好嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:22:34.92,0:22:36.78,ED_CH,,0,0,65,,{\an9\fscx90\fscy90\fad(360,360)\blur3}你聽得見我嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:22:37.71,0:22:43.46,ED_CH,,0,0,65,,{\an9\fscx90\fscy90\fad(360,360)\blur3}獨自漫步在無人的鐵道線上
Dialogue: 1,0:22:43.81,0:22:45.93,ED_CH,,0,0,65,,{\an9\fscx90\fscy90\fad(360,360)\blur3}時而嚎啕大哭
Dialogue: 1,0:22:46.71,0:22:48.75,ED_CH,,0,0,65,,{\an9\fscx90\fscy90\fad(360,360)\blur3}時而逗你歡笑
Dialogue: 1,0:22:49.38,0:22:55.24,ED_CH,,0,0,65,,{\an9\fscx90\fscy90\fad(360,360)\blur3}抱緊記憶裡不想淡去的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.24,0:23:01.63,ED_CH,,0,0,40,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}想用比告別更珍貴的話語告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.63,0:23:07.40,ED_CH,,0,0,40,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}平平無奇 卻又獨一無二
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.40,0:23:10.92,ED_CH,,0,0,40,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}那些曾經只有這雙眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.92,0:23:13.89,ED_CH,,0,0,40,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}才能看見的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.89,0:23:18.71,ED_CH,,0,0,40,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}為何如今已隨處可見？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.71,0:23:24.72,ED_CH,,0,0,40,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}所以即使 獲得了新的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.90,0:23:30.64,ED_CH,,0,0,40,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}我也還會選擇這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.64,0:23:36.64,ED_CH,,0,0,40,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}所以如果 還能與你相逢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.64,0:23:42.32,ED_CH,,0,0,40,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}那就永不分離 我還會選擇當下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.32,0:23:45.22,ED_CH,,0,0,40,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}不需要什麼約定
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.22,0:23:48.32,ED_CH,,0,0,40,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}在孤獨迷茫的日子裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.32,0:23:54.31,ED_CH,,0,0,40,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}不必強忍淚水 黎明總會到來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.54,0:23:58.54,ED_CH,,0,0,40,,{\fad(360,0)\blur3}我正哼著我們的搖籃曲 等你回家呢
Dialogue: 1,0:23:58.54,0:24:01.35,ED_CH,,0,0,65,,{\an9\fscx90\fscy90\fad(0,360)\blur3}我正哼著我們的搖籃曲 等你回家呢
